<h1>Barking Up the Wrong Tree - by Eric Barker</h1>
<small>
ISBN: 0062416049<br>
Date read: 2017-11-04<br>
How strongly I recommend it: <strong>4</strong>/10<br>
<strong>(See <a href="/book">my list of 200+ books</a>, for more.)</strong>
